To defeat the forces of gravity thanks to an adhesive and to be able to climb up walls like Superman.
This is the subject of four American research centres, one of which now seems to have almost reached its destination.
With an adhesive applied on an area of only 2.5 qcm, the researchers succeeded in fixing a 100 kg body on a vertical wall.
